### health.http — Actuator Health Contract (ADR-040)
### Validates the gateway boot and infrastructure readiness.
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Health Check — Actuator Endpoint
# @name healthCheck
GET {{$dotenv GATEWAY_TARGET_URL}}/actuator/health
Accept: application/json

?? status == 200
?? body status == UP

